  "synopsis": "Everyone knows the story of the last Jedi Knight, Luke Skywalker. But 4000 years before this solitary hero battled to save the universe the Jedi were a wandering tribe of peace keepers maintaining the balance against the dark side of the Force. This is the story of one such warrior, young Jedi Ulic Qel-Droma, as he battles the dark side power of Freedon Nadd to save the planet Onderon from being swallowed by evil!",
